# ─── Text Aura environment ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Anthropic API key for live persona transformations.
# Leave this UNSET to run the app in "Sandbox Demo Mode" — it falls back to
# curated client-side templates so the app is fully interactive out of the box.
#
# Copy this file to ".env" and drop in your key:
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# NOTE: A Vite SPA exposes any key shipped to the browser. This direct-from-browser
# setup is fine for local demos / family testing. For production, proxy requests
# through a small backend that holds the key server-side.
VITE_AI_API_KEY=
